/a>致敬。该封面是对普林斯的家乡明尼苏达州（副总统候选人蒂姆·沃尔兹担任州长的州）的致敬，并且直接在沃尔兹的主题演讲之前进行。</p><p>看看下面的视频。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="观看：史蒂夫·旺德 (Stevie Wonder) 在 2024 年民主党全国代表大会上表演 | 2024 年民主党全国委员会第三夜" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/d7WwD5xmWPA?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="约翰·传奇 (John Legend) 和希拉·E. (Sheila E.) 在民主党全国代表大会上表演" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/8w2PyMvVdTE?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>据<a href="https://edition.cnn.com/2024/08/21/entertainment/pink-john-legend-dnc/index.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>CNN 报道</em></a>，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pink">平克</a>将于今晚（8 月 22 日）结束民主党全国委员会最后一晚的闭幕式。</p><p>该活动发生在<a href="https://www.nme.com/politics/joe-biden-has-officially-stepped-down-as-the-us-democratic-presidential-candidate-3776677">即将于 11 月 5 日举行的美国总统选举</a>之前。</p><p>昨晚的节目中还包括女演员明迪·卡林、喜剧演员基南·汤普森和奥普拉·温弗瑞的演讲，奥普拉·温弗瑞是在最后一刻加入的。</p><p>来自音乐界的明星纷纷站出来支持哈里斯，包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ariana-grande">爱莉安娜·格兰德</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lizzo">利佐</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/olivia-rodrigo">奥利维亚·罗德里戈</a>——后者<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/olivia-rodrigo-throws-support-behind-kamala-harris-over-reproductive-rights-stance-3777706">强调了副总统在生殖权利方面的立场</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3777450" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3777450" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3777450" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Kamala-Harris-Photo-by-Andrew-Harnik_Getty-Images.jpg" alt="卡玛拉·哈里斯" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Kamala-Harris-Photo-by-Andrew-Harnik_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Kamala-Harris-Photo-by-Andrew-Harnik_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Kamala-Harris-Photo-by-Andrew-Harnik_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Kamala-Harris-Photo-by-Andrew-Harnik_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Kamala-Harris-Photo-by-Andrew-Harnik_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Kamala-Harris-Photo-by-Andrew-Harnik_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3777450" class="wp-caption-text">卡玛拉·哈里斯——图片来源：Andrew Harnik/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/charli-xcx-john-legend-and-more-endorse-kamala-harris-for-us-president-3776745">Charli XCX 通过发帖表示支持哈里斯</a>：“Kamala IS brat”，指的是她的新热门专辑和流行文化现象<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/charli-xcx-brat-review-lyrics-tracklist-3762875">“Brat”</a> 。这导致<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-cnn-attempt-to-explain-the-kamala-is-brat-charli-xcx-memes-3777048">美国有线电视新闻网 (CNN) 试图在直播中向观众解释</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/charli-xcx-brat-summer-timeline-highs-lows-3777880">“小孩子夏天”的</a>趋势。</p><p> 7 月，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/megan-thee-stallion">梅根·西·斯塔林 (Megan Thee Stallion)</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-megan-thee-stallion-perform-at-kamala-harris-rally-3779500">在哈里斯总统竞选活动的集会上表演</a>。“现在我知道人群中的女士们热爱她们的身体。如果你想继续热爱自己的身体，你就知道该投票给谁，”这位艺术家在谈到哈里斯对生殖权利的立场时告诉观众。</p><p>此外，前<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/migos">Migos</a>说唱歌手<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/quavo">Quavo</a>在集会上发表了演讲，讲述了哈里斯致力于解决枪支暴力问题并管理白宫首个枪支暴力预防办公室的承诺。</p><p>本月早些时候，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bon-iver">邦·艾弗（Bon Iver）</a>还<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-bon-iver-perform-at-kamala-harris-rally-in-wisconsin-3781912">表演了一场短盘来支持哈里斯在威斯康星州的集会</a>。</p><p>在其他地方， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/beyonces-freedom-soundtracks-kamala-harris-first-presidential-election-campaign-video-3777987">碧昂斯允许哈里斯在竞选视频中使用她的歌曲《自由》，</a>此前<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kamala-harris-walks-out-to-beyonces-freedom-at-first-campaign-staff-meeting-since-bidens-withdrawal-as-presidential-candidate-3776994">副总统最近在一次员工会议上在雄浑的国歌中退场</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3776995" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3776995" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3776995" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/kamala-harris-beyonce@2000x1270.jpg" alt="卡玛拉·哈里斯和碧昂斯的合成图像" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/kamala-harris-beyonce@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/kamala-harris-beyonce@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/kamala-harris-beyonce@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/kamala-harris-beyonce@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/kamala-harris-beyonce@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/kamala-harris-beyonce@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3776995" class="wp-caption-text">卡玛拉·哈里斯、碧昂斯。图片来源：ERIN SCHAFF/POOL/AFP（来自 Getty Images）和 Michael Buckner/Billboard（来自 Getty Images）</figcaption></figure><p>据报道，碧昂斯此后威胁共和党候选人<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/donald-trump">唐纳德·特朗普</a>的竞选团队<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/beyonce-reportedly-sends-trump-campaign-cease-and-desist-for-freedom-video-3785808">，因为后者在社交媒体视频中未经授权使用这首歌</a>。</p><p>据<a href="https://www.rollingstone.com